introduction: A wealthy entrepreneur invests in a young woman's project. It's her last chance to find money to fulfill her dream. He sees a chance to cut off a sense of growing emptiness. Dramatic consequences occur as he decides to exchange his wealth only if she accepts a part of his body. At first she refuses, convinced the man is crazy. But when her friend says he could accept money despite peculiar circumstances, she decides to take a chance. Maybe this is just a test.A few days later she has second thoughts. But it's too late to call it off. The man is gone. One day she receives a package of the size of a forearm.
